Hi! TweakScale maintainer here. Sorry being so late, but I just noticed your post today.

Usually things get way faster by posting on TweakScale's thread:

 

Anyway, about your problem, this is it: 

[LOG 13:00:55.847] [TweakScale] ERROR: **FATAL** Part bdWarheadSmall (Small High Explosive Warhead) has a fatal problem due having duplicated properties - see issue [#34]( https://github.com/net-lisias-ksp/TweakScale/issues/34 ). at error:0

Looking into it, I found: 

[LOG 12:57:18.808] Applying update BDArmory/MMPatches/000000_HitpointModule/@PART[*] to BDArmory/Parts/smallWarhead/part.cfg/PART[bdWarheadSmall]
[LOG 12:57:18.868] Applying update BDArmory/MMPatches/000000_HitpointModule/@PART[*] to TOP GUNS/GameData/BDArmory/Parts/smallWarhead/part.cfg/PART[bdWarheadSmall]
[LOG 12:57:19.185] Applying update BDArmory/MMPatches/BDArmory_TweakScale /@PART[bdWarheadSmall] to BDArmory/Parts/smallWarhead/part.cfg/PART[bdWarheadSmall]
[LOG 12:57:19.186] Applying update BDArmory/MMPatches/BDArmory_TweakScale /@PART[bdWarheadSmall] to TOP GUNS/GameData/BDArmory/Parts/smallWarhead/part.cfg/PART[bdWarheadSmall]
[LOG 12:57:19.202] Applying update BDArmory/MMPatches/BDA_TweakScale/@PART[bdWarheadSmall] to BDArmory/Parts/smallWarhead/part.cfg/PART[bdWarheadSmall]
[LOG 12:57:19.203] Applying update BDArmory/MMPatches/BDA_TweakScale/@PART[bdWarheadSmall] to TOP GUNS/GameData/BDArmory/Parts/smallWarhead/part.cfg/PART[bdWarheadSmall]

I think you installed some add'ns on the wrong place, theres a BDArmory copy installed on 

C:\Program Files\Epic Games\KerbalSpaceProgram\English\TOP GUNS/GameData/BDArmory/

and another on :

C:\Program Files\Epic Games\KerbalSpaceProgram\English\GameData/BDArmory/

Remove the directory called "TOP GUNS" from your KSP and things should be fine - this extra copy is probably screwing up something else...
